dict.acceptation: 正常地；通常地，一般地；按说；论理；

sent.orig: The first lining is normally mull, the second lining normally kraft.
sent.trans: 第一层通常是纱布，第二层是牛皮纸。

sent.orig: Transmission standard: normally closed, normally open and pneumatic.
sent.trans: 驱动装置标准：常闭型、常开型、及气动型。

sent.orig: Audits can be "Normally On" or "Normally Off "
sent.trans: 审计可以被“一般”或“正常起飞”

sent.orig: Measure current-Model 7169A relays remain normally open and Model 7158 relays go to normally open.
sent.trans: 测量电流——7169A型继电器仍保持在常开位置，7158型继电器连接至常开触点。

sent.orig: Normally closed switches, less common than normally open, are made in one of two ways.
sent.trans: 常闭开关没有常开开关那么常见，它是采用两种方式之一制成的。
